# Product Schema

## Core Product Models

The product system consists of several related models:

- [Product](mdc:src/api/product/content-types/product/schema.json) - The main product model
  - Has attributes like Title, Description, CoverImage, Media, Status
  - Related to categories, variations, reviews, tags, FAQs
  
- [Product Variation](mdc:src/api/product-variation/content-types/product-variation/schema.json) - Represents different variants of a product
  - Connected to product variation colors and sizes
  - Contains pricing, stock, and SKU information
  
- [Product Variation Model](mdc:src/api/product-variation-model/content-types/product-variation-model/schema.json) - Model templates for product variations
  
## Product Categorization
  
- [Product Category](mdc:src/api/product-category/content-types/product-category/schema.json) - Hierarchical categories for products
  - Can be main category or additional categories for products
  - Contains fields like Name, Image, ParentCategory
  
- [Product Category Content](mdc:src/api/product-category-content/content-types/product-category-content/schema.json) - Content for product categories

- [Product Tag](mdc:src/api/product-tag/content-types/product-tag/schema.json) - Tags for product filtering and organization

## Product Variants

- [Product Variation Color](mdc:src/api/product-variation-color/content-types/product-variation-color/schema.json) - Color options for product variations
- [Product Variation Size](mdc:src/api/product-variation-size/content-types/product-variation-size/schema.json) - Size options for product variations
- [Product Size Helper](mdc:src/api/product-size-helper/content-types/product-size-helper/schema.json) - Size guide for products

## Product Feedback

- [Product Review](mdc:src/api/product-review/content-types/product-review/schema.json) - Customer reviews for products
- [Product Review Reply](mdc:src/api/product-review-reply/content-types/product-review-reply/schema.json) - Replies to product reviews
- [Product Review Like](mdc:src/api/product-review-like/content-types/product-review-like/schema.json) - Likes on product reviews
- [Product Like](mdc:src/api/product-like/content-types/product-like/schema.json) - User likes for products
- [Product FAQ](mdc:src/api/product-faq/content-types/product-faq/schema.json) - Frequently asked questions about products

## Product Inventory

- [Product Stock](mdc:src/api/product-stock/content-types/product-stock/schema.json) - Stock management for products
- [Product Stock Log](mdc:src/api/product-stock-log/content-types/product-stock-log/schema.json) - Logs of stock changes

